Card data attribution
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Magic: The Gathering card data is sourced from Scryfall
(https://scryfall.com/docs/api) bulk data, used under Scryfall's terms.

This project bundles NO card data. The Scryfall bulk dataset (~60k cards) is
downloaded locally on first run; it is not redistributed as part of this
repository or any release artifact.

